overview: ShoXC was a mixed martial arts series produced by the mixed martial arts organization EliteXC, Showtime and Proelite.com. The purpose of the show is to highlight up and coming MMA fighters. This event took place on October 26, 2007 on Showtime at the Chumash Casino in Santa Ynez, California.
title: ShoXC 3: Hamman vs. Rosa
